1.0.name: wordpress/zbplayer
1.0.description: zbPlayer is a very easy audio plugin - you can select some options like: include Download link or no, enable autoplay or no and setup width of player. Other things will be done by zbPlayer plugun automatically. One nice feature - player support cyrillic filenames without problem. Also player can share your mp3 files on Facebook.
